~ start
if GlobalStorage.game_data.friend_revealed:
	Suika: Yes? Suiyobi~
	You: [#default]...
	=> END
match GlobalStorage.game_data.current_stage:
	when 0
		%
			Suika: [#default]Girl your room is so nice and warm~
			You: Well that's because my aircon's broken.
			You: Plus, when did you start liking the warm weather?
			Suika: [#playful]Well, summer's always the season for change!
		%
			You: [#sad]Listen, Sui... I'm sorry for what happened a few days ago.
			You: If you ever need help, or a place to stay, I'll always be there for you!
			You: [#happy]I'm glad you seem all okay though!
			Suika: [#default]What do you mean? Of course I'm okay!
			Suika: The summer sun melts away all unhappiness and sorrow~
	when 1
		%
			Suika: [#default]Why did you have to break your TV?
			You: There was something weird inside it, like some kind of eye.
			You: I swear it was making the room hotter.
			Suika: Having an eye in something doesn't mean you have to break it!
			Suika: What if you hurt somebody doing it?
			You: But it was just me in my house...?
		%
			Suika: [#playful]It's so nice and sunny out, you should really stop bumming around in your house the whole day!
			You: [#default]Maybe it's because it's so "nice" and "sunny" that I'm staying inside?!
	when 2
		%
			You:[#default]How are you wearing a jacket in this weather?
			You: I swear it's abnormally hot out here.
			Suika: Really? It's not even that hot silly~
			You: Seriously what's gotten into you today?
			You: Usually you're the one complaining about the heat in this kinda weather.
			Suika: I just learnt to love summer I guess, teehee~
		%
			You: [#default]I swear there's something wrong with the street lamps.
			You: It feels as if I'm being boiled alive under them.
			Suika: It's probably just a side effect from you all holing up inside when it's summer.
			Suika: Try staying under the lamps longer to get used to them!
		%
			You: [#default]Isn't it strange that there is no one on the streets at all?
			You: It's so... Quiet...
			Suika: Isn't it better this way?
			Suika: Just the two of us, and the beautiful sun.
			Suika: Foreve-
			You: Sorry?
			
	when 3
		%
			You: [#default]Remember when we bought your first skirt at that store?
			You: You were so unsure of yourself, but I knew you would rock it!
			Suika: Yes! And now, all my insecurities are washed away, by this gentle sun~
			You: What's with you and the sun lately?
			You: I'm glad you're feeling better though.
		%
			You: [#default]There's such limited shopping options here.
			You: We should totally move to the city together one day!
			Suika: Why? The beach, the park, the weather.
			Suika: Everything is so nice here!
			You: Don't you want to get more cute clothes?
			Suika: I have a higher calling now~
			You: [#confused]...?

		
=> END

~ killed

Suika: Oh Suiyobi...
Suika: You cannot kill me in a meaningful way...
You: [#scared]Ahhh...
do GameBus.call_pixel_sort.emit()
You: [#shocked]AHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH[next=1.0]



=> END

~ eldritch_whispers

%
	Suika: I love you, Suiyobi~
%
	Suika: I miss you.
%
	Suika: Am I pretty?
%
	Suika: No more darkness, no more suffering.
%
	Suika: Summer is the season of change~
%
	Suika: Don't you recognise me?
	
=> END